to take my family and live in hiding.

566
00:30:45,530 --> 00:30:46,890
The letter included this.

567
00:30:48,230 --> 00:30:49,510
He told me to keep it safe,

568
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:50,820
saying

569
00:30:50,870 --> 00:30:52,590
it might come in handy someday.

570
00:30:58,740 --> 00:30:59,550
Secretary Wu,

571
00:31:00,890 --> 00:31:02,170
I must investigate

572
00:31:02,190 --> 00:31:03,600
Ke Jingping's secret room.

573
00:31:03,830 --> 00:31:05,590
If this is his biggest secret,

574
00:31:05,710 --> 00:31:08,260
it won't be easy to infiltrate.

575
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:10,670
The danger will be immense.

576
00:31:10,670 --> 00:31:11,950
I have to go no matter how dangerous it is.

577
00:31:12,550 --> 00:31:14,990
It's the only way to confirm Ke Jingping's true identity

578
00:31:14,990 --> 00:31:16,960
and verify whether my deductions are correct.

579
00:31:19,820 --> 00:31:21,540
Because the intelligence Myna held

580
00:31:22,390 --> 00:31:24,790
concerns the life and death of all of Changsha.

581
00:31:29,950 --> 00:31:30,750
Ke Jingping.

582
00:31:31,340 --> 00:31:32,860
Say it again!

583
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:35,080
What exactly do you mean by "soon"?

584
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:35,800
Three days.

585
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:36,590
Within three days,

586
00:31:36,590 --> 00:31:38,210
I'll deliver the intelligence to you.

587
00:31:38,420 --> 00:31:39,000
Good.

588
00:31:39,300 --> 00:31:40,540
I hope you can keep your promise.

589
00:31:44,510 --> 00:31:45,110
Commander,

590
00:31:45,320 --> 00:31:46,440
the Japanese are advancing aggressively.

591
00:31:46,510 --> 00:31:47,980
Let me send my troops into battle!

592
00:31:51,740 --> 00:31:52,360
No.

593
00:31:54,450 --> 00:31:56,320
Your unit is my final reserve.

594
00:31:58,090 --> 00:31:58,890
Guys,

595
00:32:00,830 --> 00:32:03,870
the Japanese have been launching frontal assaults on us,

596
00:32:04,390 --> 00:32:07,160
but their real strength lies in flanking maneuvers.

597
00:32:07,630 --> 00:32:10,020
They're likely to bypass our defenses

598
00:32:10,390 --> 00:32:11,520
and attack us from behind.

599
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,810
They've done this in Shanghai,

600
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:15,800
Nanjing, Wuhan, and Taiyuan.

601
00:32:15,830 --> 00:32:16,630
Which direction do you think

602
00:32:16,770 --> 00:32:18,560
they'll come from this time?

603
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:20,280
The Japanese 3rd Division

604
00:32:20,820 --> 00:32:22,660
has been stationed across from Yueyang Lake,

605
00:32:22,910 --> 00:32:24,550
delaying their engagement in the frontal attack.

606
00:32:24,990 --> 00:32:25,790
I suspect

607
00:32:25,970 --> 00:32:28,240
they may cross Yueyang Lake

608
00:32:28,500 --> 00:32:29,590
to flank us and head for Changsha.

609
00:32:30,230 --> 00:32:32,410
Then I'll position my troops on the western front to wait for them.

610
00:32:34,710 --> 00:32:37,470
But we mustn't ignore the Eastern side either,

611
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,160
where the Japanese 106th Division is positioned.

612
00:32:39,230 --> 00:32:40,500
The 106th Division?

613
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:42,370
They've already been defeated by me once.

614
00:32:42,650 --> 00:32:44,000
Last year, at Wanjialing,

615
00:32:44,190 --> 00:32:45,780
I almost wiped them out.

616
00:32:46,540 --> 00:32:50,620
Okamura Yasuji is a crafty old fox.

617
00:32:51,090 --> 00:32:52,430
If I don't get reliable

618
00:32:52,430 --> 00:32:53,830
intelligence soon,

619
00:32:53,950 --> 00:32:56,410
I absolutely can't deploy your troops yet.

620
00:33:05,820 --> 00:33:07,100
Commander,

621
00:33:07,270 --> 00:33:09,310
the 6th Division's frontal assault has stalled.

622
00:33:09,330 --> 00:33:10,650
The 13th Division reports

623
00:33:10,870 --> 00:33:12,710
Chinese forces are counterattacking the front.

624
00:33:12,750 --> 00:33:14,150
The 33rd Division reports

625
00:33:14,230 --> 00:33:16,100
severe casualties in our ranks.

626
00:33:16,520 --> 00:33:17,480
Commander.

627
00:33:17,680 --> 00:33:19,510
If the frontal attack continues to fail,

628
00:33:19,630 --> 00:33:21,550
our flanking forces

629
00:33:21,570 --> 00:33:22,970
must act immediately.

630
00:33:23,350 --> 00:33:24,950
The 106th Division is fully assembled

631
00:33:25,050 --> 00:33:26,090
and requests to engage.

632
00:33:31,630 --> 00:33:32,950
Send a telegram to Kunwu.

633
00:33:33,350 --> 00:33:34,950
This Hunting Operation

634
00:33:35,340 --> 00:33:36,500
must end

635
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:37,610
as quickly as possible.

636
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:38,480
Yes.

637
00:33:46,270 --> 00:33:50,100
[By sunset tomorrow, the intelligence must reach the Ninth War Zone]

638
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,600
Have these been thoroughly reviewed?

639
00:34:15,630 --> 00:34:16,590
There's no repeat, right?

640
00:34:18,429 --> 00:34:19,090
Sir.

641
00:34:19,120 --> 00:34:20,199
This is the last batch.

642
00:34:21,080 --> 00:34:21,889
Okay.

643
00:34:27,310 --> 00:34:28,280
Come on,

644
00:34:28,429 --> 00:34:29,800
just answer what the officer asks.

645
00:34:29,830 --> 00:34:30,659
Cut the crap.

646
00:34:30,710 --> 00:34:32,190
You're wasting everyone's time.

647
00:34:32,770 --> 00:34:33,980
Come on!

648
00:34:34,010 --> 00:34:35,560
You're all bullying me!

649
00:34:35,620 --> 00:34:36,480
Let me tell you,

650
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:37,750
I'm just a woman

651
00:34:37,790 --> 00:34:39,870
who traveled all alone on a long boat ride.

652
00:34:40,310 --> 00:34:42,030
I vomited the whole way, you know?

653
00:34:42,909 --> 00:34:43,710
It's her!

654
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:50,010
You came at the right time.

655
00:34:50,239 --> 00:34:51,840
I found the real Mister.

656
00:34:52,239 --> 00:34:54,409
She's the daughter-in-law of the fabric shop in Chaye Alley,

657
00:34:54,870 --> 00:34:55,969
named Xu Zhaodi.

658
00:34:56,210 --> 00:34:58,010
Her situation aligns with your analysis.

659
00:34:58,030 --> 00:34:59,040
She said her husband was dead

660
00:34:59,100 --> 00:35:00,070
and she returned to live with her in-laws.

661
00:35:09,480 --> 00:35:10,270
Stop. Stop.

662
00:35:10,290 --> 00:35:10,950
Wait.

663
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:24,990
She's gone.

664
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:26,470
Alright, I got it.

665
00:35:26,470 --> 00:35:26,880
Go ahead.

666
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:27,410
Yes.

667
00:35:36,230 --> 00:35:36,910
Director Xu.

668
00:35:36,910 --> 00:35:38,510
Tell me about what you've found so far.

669
00:35:38,660 --> 00:35:39,260
Okay.

670
00:35:40,750 --> 00:35:42,590
At 2:38 a.m. today,

671
00:35:42,900 --> 00:35:44,380
a suspicious signal was detected,

672
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:46,230
identical to the one intercepted

673
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:47,380
on the night Yang Ziming was killed.

674
00:35:48,310 --> 00:35:49,350
Based on the signal,

675
00:35:49,470 --> 00:35:51,310
we've narrowed down the transmission area,

676
00:35:51,560 --> 00:35:53,790
and Xu Zhaodi's fabric shop falls within it.

677
00:35:54,910 --> 00:35:55,510
Chief.

678
00:35:55,990 --> 00:35:57,270
Before reporting

679
00:35:57,270 --> 00:35:58,320
to your office,

680
00:35:58,790 --> 00:35:59,590
I sent someone

681
00:35:59,590 --> 00:36:01,150
to check on her shop.

682
00:36:01,630 --> 00:36:03,090
They reported that she was no longer there.

683
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:05,280
Her father-in-law was watching the store today.

684
00:36:05,430 --> 00:36:06,110
I think

685
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:07,790
it's necessary to search the place.

686
00:36:07,990 --> 00:36:09,630
Given how long she's been active,

687
00:36:09,940 --> 00:36:11,920
there's bound to be useful information."

688
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:14,540
Fine. Take your team there.

689
00:36:15,150 --> 00:36:16,270
Don't disappoint me.

690
00:36:16,750 --> 00:36:17,310
Yes.

691
00:36:19,910 --> 00:36:20,950
It's just as I suspected.

692
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:22,820
He's deploying all capable

693
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:23,870
operatives from the station.

694
00:36:40,580 --> 00:36:41,150
Hello?

695
00:36:45,110 --> 00:36:45,740
Okay.

696
00:36:52,390 --> 00:36:54,110
Ji Fang ran into Mi Lan on his way

697
00:36:54,630 --> 00:36:55,520
to the police station.

698
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:58,470
What? That's bold of them.

699
00:36:59,190 --> 00:36:59,910
Chief.

700
00:37:01,260 --> 00:37:04,140
That's near Ling Han's safehouse.

701
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:06,850
He must've arranged it beforehand,

702
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:08,750
knowing that once he was gone,

703
00:37:08,750 --> 00:37:09,790
we'd avoid

704
00:37:09,790 --> 00:37:11,360
his residences and safehouses.

705
00:37:18,670 --> 00:37:19,320
Chief.

706
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:20,590
I'll go bring them back.

707
00:37:20,630 --> 00:37:21,380
I'll go too.

708
00:37:21,630 --> 00:37:22,230
Fine.

709
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:23,110
But remember,

710
00:37:23,650 --> 00:37:24,480
I want them alive.

711
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:25,520
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

712
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:39,920
Don't you find this whole situation suspicious?

713
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:42,740
You mean how Mi Lan was conveniently spotted by Ji Fang?

714
00:37:44,950 --> 00:37:45,750
Exactly.

715
00:37:46,860 --> 00:37:47,790
What do you plan to do?

716
00:37:50,240 --> 00:37:52,000
They've likely set something up over there,

717
00:37:53,030 --> 00:37:54,690
but we can't rule out other moves.

718
00:37:55,260 --> 00:37:56,460
We need to split up.

719
00:37:57,270 --> 00:37:58,270
Most of our capable operatives

720
00:37:58,270 --> 00:37:59,350
have been sent out.

721
00:38:00,430 --> 00:38:01,430
The station is

722
00:38:01,430 --> 00:38:02,620
practically defenseless.

723
00:38:03,110 --> 00:38:04,590
They're sure to exploit the weakness.

724
00:38:06,560 --> 00:38:07,410
I'll stay.

725
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:08,960
You handle the situation over there.

726
00:38:09,720 --> 00:38:10,850
Maybe I should stay instead.

727
00:38:11,120 --> 00:38:12,790
Dealing with someone like Mi Lan requires strategy.

728
00:38:13,100 --> 00:38:14,480
A direct confrontation isn't the best approach.

729
00:38:15,810 --> 00:38:17,330
If he really wanted to stay,

730
00:38:17,670 --> 00:38:19,710
he wouldn't be explaining all this.

731
00:38:20,340 --> 00:38:22,240
He'd be trying to trick me into leaving instead.

732
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:25,160
I'm exploiting my concern,

733
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:26,960
making you think the other side is more dangerous,

734
00:38:28,020 --> 00:38:29,020
so you'll choose to go there.

735
00:38:29,390 --> 00:38:31,130
Mi Lan's target today is here.

736
00:38:31,890 --> 00:38:33,960
I can't let you stay and face that risk.

737
00:38:36,630 --> 00:38:37,790
Then you stay.

738
00:38:37,980 --> 00:38:38,730
I'll go handle the other side.

739
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:43,150
Or

740
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:44,930
you stay here.

741
00:38:44,950 --> 00:38:45,940
I'll make it quick.

742
00:38:46,750 --> 00:38:48,220
As soon as I'm done,

743
00:38:48,250 --> 00:38:49,140
I'll return to help you.

744
00:38:50,870 --> 00:38:51,630
Take a larger team with you.

745
00:38:51,630 --> 00:38:52,380
And be careful.

746
00:38:54,390 --> 00:38:55,190
Director Xu.

747
00:38:55,210 --> 00:38:56,090
The provincial government has a meeting

748
00:38:56,120 --> 00:38:57,860
to discuss internal security.

749
00:38:58,790 --> 00:38:59,830
I won't be going,

750
00:39:00,030 --> 00:39:00,830
so you go instead.

751
00:39:01,150 --> 00:39:01,650
Yes.

752
00:39:01,950 --> 00:39:02,590
Yes, Chief.

753
00:39:11,670 --> 00:39:12,310
Qiu.

754
00:39:12,790 --> 00:39:13,980
I need to attend a meeting at the provincial government.

755
00:39:14,070 --> 00:39:14,570
The direction finder

756
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:16,090
will be here soon.

757
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:16,890
Keep it for me.

758
00:39:17,070 --> 00:39:18,890
I'll calibrate it myself once I return.

759
00:39:19,710 --> 00:39:20,320
Thank you.

760
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:40,250
It's her.

761
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:43,450
Madam.

762
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:44,490
Everything's arranged.

763
00:39:44,870 --> 00:39:45,470
Move!

764
00:40:25,100 --> 00:40:26,190
Where are Mi Lan and Zong Fang?

765
00:40:28,030 --> 00:40:28,660
Retreat!

766
00:40:33,910 --> 00:40:34,710
Madam!

767
00:40:55,660 --> 00:40:56,540
Please wait a moment.

768
00:41:45,250 --> 00:41:47,200
[Bureau of Investigation and Statistics]

769
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:08,640
Leader Yun.

770
00:42:08,670 --> 00:42:09,740
What was just delivered?

771
00:42:09,780 --> 00:42:11,260
It's the direction finder from Chongqing.

772
00:42:11,310 --> 00:42:11,830
Made in the UK.

773
00:42:11,850 --> 00:42:13,530
I've already had Director Xu's people take it.

774
00:42:18,590 --> 00:42:19,350
I'm Yun Hongshen

775
00:42:19,350 --> 00:42:20,030
Leader Yun.

776
00:42:20,030 --> 00:42:20,830
Anything I can help with?

777
00:42:21,520 --> 00:42:23,120
What's with the direction finder from Chongqing?

778
00:42:23,790 --> 00:42:25,640
We were notified early this morning

779
00:42:25,670 --> 00:42:27,550
that it was on its way,

780
00:42:27,570 --> 00:42:28,210
Well,

781
00:42:28,240 --> 00:42:29,310
we just received it.

782
00:42:29,340 --> 00:42:31,100
You are so well-informed.

783
00:42:31,130 --> 00:42:32,090
Where did you put it?

784
00:42:32,110 --> 00:42:32,910
In the warehouse.

785
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:47,640
Stop!

786
00:42:56,960 --> 00:42:57,820
[In Operation]
